      <event start="T458" end="T459">zej nimaš več tak, </event>
      <event start="T459" end="T1580-592">ne? </event>
      <event start="T1580-592" end="T1582-249">Proti konc mesca. </event>
      <event start="T1593-159" end="T1594-249">Sej vem. </event>
      <event start="T1603-792" end="T1605-052">Aja, </event>
      <event start="T1605-052" end="T1606-966">včeri ste pa bli eee v Mariboru. </event>
      <event start="T1608-333" end="T1609-455">Šla kej v šoping? </event>
      <event start="T1614-306" end="T474">Si si? </event>
      <event start="T474" end="T475">No, </event>
      <event start="T475" end="T1615-844">fajn. </event>
      <event start="T1617-124" end="T1618-028">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1624-242" end="T1626-117">T@t ma take lepe s() ... </event>
      <event start="T1626-624" end="T1627-575">Sam tut cenovno kr drage, </event>
      <event start="T1627-575" end="T1628-487">ne? </event>
      <event start="T1633-255" end="T1634-408">Cenovno? </event>
      <event start="T1637-353" end="T1638-177">Grejo. </event>
      <event start="T1640-963" end="T1642-073">Ka si si pa kupla? </event>
      <event start="T1642-073" end="T490">Mi povej. </event>
      <event start="T490" end="T1643-737">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1645-829" end="T1647-038">Hlače, majca? </event>
      <event start="T1652-032" end="T1653-035">Nobenih hlač? </event>
      <event start="T1653-035" end="T1654-711">Hlače rabiš zdej. </event>
      <event start="T1663-886" end="T503">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T503" end="T1665-027">sej fajn. </event>
      <event start="T1670-239" end="T1671-65">Goro stvari, k ti ... </event>
      <event start="T1678-102" end="T1678-689">To je res. </event>
      <event start="T1678-689" end="T1682-016">Js sn si tud dans n() kupla nove olstrartke. </event>
      <event start="T1682-957" end="T1683-306">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1685-24" end="T515">Sej si vsak let kupim. </event>
      <event start="T515" end="T1688-422">Vsak let si e() bele. </event>
      <event start="T1688-422" end="T1688-989">Bele, </event>
      <event start="T1688-989" end="T1689-449">pazi. </event>
      <event start="T1689-837" end="T1690-888">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T1690-888" end="T1691-653">z mal platforme. </event>
      <event start="T1692-457" end="T516">Eee </event>
      <event start="T516" end="T1693-38">mal, </event>
      <event start="T1693-38" end="T1693-669">ja. </event>
      <event start="T1693-669" end="T1694-521">Nimam rada. </event>
      <event start="T1695-325" end="T1695-682">Tako, </event>
      <event start="T1695-682" end="T518">mal, </event>
      <event start="T518" end="T519">ja, </event>
      <event start="T519" end="T520">to. </event>
      <event start="T520" end="T1697-239">Bele rabim. </event>
      <event start="T1697-239" end="T1700-758">Sss ... ful več. </event>
      <event start="T1700-758" end="T1701-345">In v() ... </event>
      <event start="T1701-345" end="T521">Aja, </event>
      <event start="T521" end="T1702-764">podplate. </event>
      <event start="T1705-233" end="T1707-543">Tiste, ko mam js ful debele, narezlane? </event>
      <event start="T1708-237" end="T525">A veš, </event>
      <event start="T525" end="T1710-23">one, ko mam, rjave, črne? </event>
      <event start="T1711-677" end="T1712-343">Nis še vidla? </event>
      <event start="T1712-85" end="T527">Črne so, </event>
      <event start="T527" end="T1716-012">ampak podplat ma rjav pa črn. </event>
      <event start="T1719-975" end="T1720-958">Črno-bele, </event>
      <event start="T1720-958" end="T1722-843">sam podplat je pa rjav. </event>
      <event start="T1723-239" end="T1723-781">No, </event>
      <event start="T1723-781" end="T1724-994">tist so kr debel podplat. </event>
      <event start="T1724-994" end="T530">Zej sn si pa čist take navadne, </event>
      <event start="T530" end="T531">niso tiste obične, </event>
      <event start="T531" end="T533">ko eee vsak kamenček čutiš, </event>
      <event start="T533" end="T1730-181">ko greš po tleh, </event>
      <event start="T1730-181" end="T532">ne. </event>
      <event start="T532" end="T1732-421">Mal, mal debelejš. </event>
      <event start="T1733-451" end="T534">Glede na to, da sn skoz na nogih, </event>
      <event start="T534" end="T535">rabim mal eee platforme, </event>
      <event start="T535" end="T1737-533">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1738-639" end="T1739-296">Ne? </event>
      <event start="T1743-497" end="T1744-448">Js tut. </event>
      <event start="T1744-448" end="T1747-507">Sam ne mi pozabit dat indukcije. [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1752-243" end="T1752-778">Bravo. </event>
      <event start="T1758-029" end="T565">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T565" end="T1759-574">pa otroc. </event>
      <event start="T1761-417" end="T1762-13">Super. </event>
      <event start="T1762-606" end="T1763-498">Super. </event>
      <event start="T1765-895" end="T542">Ej, </event>
      <event start="T542" end="T1767-322">tut teb. </event>
      <event start="T1768-65" end="T1769-363">Grema? </event>
      <event start="T1769-363" end="T543">Grema, </event>
      <event start="T543" end="T1771-404">ajde. </event>
    </tier>
    <tier id="TIE1_NORM1" speaker="ROG-dialog-0011" category="norm" type="t" display-name="ROG-dialog-0011 [norm]">
      <event start="T1-288" end="T2-199">Hej. </event>
      <event start="T3-785" end="T5-085">Kako si? </event>
      <event start="T8-03" end="T2">Jaz tudi. </event>
      <event start="T2" end="T544">Veš, </event>
      <event start="T544" end="T10-638">kaj ti moram povedati. </event>
      <event start="T11-403" end="T3">Aaa. </event>
      <event start="T3" end="T545">Veš, </event>
      <event start="T545" end="T14-546">kaj sem danes delala? </event>
      <event start="T16-797" end="T18-691">Kuhinjo sem žagala. </event>
      <event start="T20-435" end="T5">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T5" end="T23-229">z vbodno žago. </event>
      <event start="T26-015" end="T26-423">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T27-739" end="T8">Carica, </event>
      <event start="T8" end="T28-465">ne? </event>
      <event start="T32-994" end="T34-784">Pol kuhinje sem zdaj stran dala, </event>
      <event start="T34-784" end="T36-412">odrezala, </event>
      <event start="T36-412" end="T39-779">z eee vbodno žago. </event>
      <event start="T39-779" end="T41-837">Prestavila v dnevno, </event>
      <event start="T41-837" end="T43-815">zdaj pa ne znam indukcije skupaj sestaviti. </event>
      <event start="T45-618" end="T13">Eee mož mi je pomagal. </event>
      <event start="T13" end="T49-078">Ja, ja, ja, ja. </event>
      <event start="T52-236" end="T53-893">Pa ploščice dol, </event>
      <event start="T53-893" end="T55-161">moram dol dati. </event>
      <event start="T55-161" end="T15">Pa bo kmalu, </event>
      <event start="T15" end="T16">čez štiri tedne bo že nova kuhinja, </event>
      <event start="T16" end="T58-153">veš? </event>
      <event start="T62-314" end="T64-027">Saj zato sem prišla k tebi. </event>
      <event start="T65-307" end="T19">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T19" end="T68-081">zato sem prišla k tebi, da mi posodiš jo. </event>
      <event start="T71-073" end="T23">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T23" end="T72-413">hvala ti. </event>
      <event start="T74-719" end="T76-315">Uporabiš, ne? </event>
      <event start="T76-315" end="T77-129">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T77-129" end="T78-17">Ampak včeraj, </event>
      <event start="T78-17" end="T80-763">včeraj sem pa pečico dol nesla. </event>
      <event start="T81-488" end="T24">Iz četrtega štuka dol. </event>
      <event start="T24" end="T85-253">Ne moreš verjeti. </event>
      <event start="T86-977" end="T87-995">Z možem. </event>
      <event start="T88-505" end="T90-095">Ja, ja, ja. </event>
      <event start="T92-399" end="T94-142">Štiri, štiri. </event>
      <event start="T97-908" end="T98-779">Pa ga ni. </event>
      <event start="T98-779" end="T99-375">Pa dobro, </event>
      <event start="T99-375" end="T29">sem hotela otroka porabiti, </event>
      <event start="T29" end="T30">ampak potem nisem. </event>
      <event start="T30" end="T102-723">Sem rekla, </event>
      <event start="T102-723" end="T103-872">bom raje počakala. </event>
      <event start="T103-872" end="T104-224">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T105-172" end="T106-911">Danes pa že kar na odpad. </event>
      <event start="T107-517" end="T108-013">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T110-403" end="T114-477">V kuhinji je še ena eee zgornja, </event>
      <event start="T114-477" end="T116-078">eee psiha. </event>
      <event start="T116-078" end="T116-922">Omarica. </event>
      <event start="T116-922" end="T117-882">Element ta zgornji, </event>
      <event start="T118-527" end="T32">eee </event>
      <event start="T32" end="T120-628">pa pol spodnje. </event>
      <event start="T120-628" end="T122-602">Umivalnik pa pomivalec pa miza. </event>
      <event start="T124-932" end="T125-832">Krožnike ... </event>
      <event start="T125-832" end="T129-339">Tisto bom stran dala v ... v dnevno. </event>
      <event start="T129-339" end="T33">V dnevno bom dala </event>
      <event start="T33" end="T133-254">pa bom ku() v dnevni kuhala. </event>
      <event start="T134-951" end="T550">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T550" end="T136-610">za štiri tedne. </event>
      <event start="T139-346" end="T141-624">Prenosna kuhinja. </event>
      <event start="T145-389" end="T149-127">Kuhinja bo dvaindvajsetega jo pripeljejo četrtega. </event>
      <event start="T149-733" end="T150-533">Aprila. </event>
      <event start="T151-132" end="T153-456">Triindvajsetega jo sestavljajo. </event>
      <event start="T154-714" end="T157-092">Petindvajsetega imam pa dopust, da kuham. </event>
      <event start="T159-402" end="T160-86">Bom, bom. </event>
      <event start="T160-86" end="T161-367">Bom. </event>
      <event start="T162-834" end="T40">Ja, ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T40" end="T164-748">verjetno kako mongolsko, </event>
      <event start="T164-748" end="T166-175">k jo imate vsi radi. </event>
      <event start="T166-175" end="T166-638">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T168-077" end="T168-446">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T169-587" end="T171-228">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T172-454" end="T174-948">Mongolsko pa en dober vinček zraven, </event>
      <event start="T174-948" end="T175-295">ne? </event>
      <event start="T178-444" end="T179-177">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T179-177" end="T180-090">čisto enostavno. </event>
      <event start="T181-579" end="T183-349">Eee. </event>
      <event start="T183-349" end="T43">Ja, mora biti, </event>
      <event start="T43" end="T185-97">najprej mora biti fajni meso. </event>
      <event start="T186-862" end="T189-021">Pol ga pa tako na majhne koščke narežeš, </event>
      <event start="T189-021" end="T190-21">lepo stolčeš. </event>
      <event start="T191-391" end="T192-631">Ful stolčeš. </event>
      <event start="T192-631" end="T45">Eee </event>
      <event start="T45" end="T199-25">pol pa daš sojino, ostrigino omako pa pa eee olje pa vino belo. </event>
      <event start="T199-896" end="T200-958">Belo. </event>
      <event start="T200-958" end="T46">Par žlic, </event>
      <event start="T46" end="T202-717">nič več. </event>
      <event start="T203-105" end="T205-871">Potem pa daš to v hladilnik. </event>
      <event start="T205-871" end="T207-298">Za štiri ure. </event>
      <event start="T207-298" end="T208-083">Počiv(), </event>
      <event start="T208-083" end="T208-749">v pac. </event>
      <event start="T209-593" end="T210-259">Tako. </event>
      <event start="T211-935" end="T49">Pol pa vsako </event>
      <event start="T49" end="T48">pol pa p() spečeš to meso, </event>
      <event start="T48" end="T216-834">med tem cajtom pa narežeš por. </event>
      <event start="T217-539" end="T50">Pa </event>
      <event start="T50" end="T51">eee </event>
      <event start="T51" end="T220-523">česen olupiš. </event>
      <event start="T221-534" end="T52">Tisti meso, </event>
      <event start="T52" end="T53">ko ga pa pečeš, </event>
      <event start="T53" end="T225-271">moraš pa po žlico peči. </event>
      <event start="T225-271" end="T54">Ker se mon() eee </event>
      <event start="T54" end="T229-06">stisne se skupaj, veš eee ... </event>
      <event start="T229-06" end="T232-851">Tako pacasto pride od eee sojine pa ostrigine omake. </event>
      <event start="T235-952" end="T55">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T55" end="T237-232">ful olja. </event>
      <event start="T240-183" end="T240-789">Mhm. </event>
      <event start="T240-789" end="T56">Po malem, </event>
      <event start="T56" end="T57">po žlico moraš </event>
      <event start="T57" end="T243-663">in to pol traja. </event>
      <event start="T244-666" end="T247-327">Pa šprica, tako da moraš imeti obvezno pokrovko. </event>
      <event start="T247-327" end="T248-479">Pa okrog. </event>
      <event start="T248-479" end="T249-589">Za ... </event>
      <event start="T250-837" end="T251-405">Pol pa por, </event>
      <event start="T251-405" end="T253-71">ampak samo zelen del od pora. </event>
      <event start="T254-661" end="T256-845">Nič onega stebla, ko je bel. </event>
      <event start="T256-845" end="T259-025">Samo zeleni del na take trakce narežeš, </event>
      <event start="T259-025" end="T260-269">potem pa </event>
      <event start="T260-269" end="T58">eee </event>
      <event start="T58" end="T262-916">malo prepražiš česenčka, </event>
      <event start="T262-916" end="T264-006">daš meso not, </event>
      <event start="T264-006" end="T264-847">pomešaš s porom vred, </event>
      <event start="T264-847" end="T267-217">riž še vmes skuhaš. </event>
      <event start="T269-915" end="T271-045">Čakaš, ne? </event>
      <event start="T271-045" end="T271-731">Saj bo, </event>
      <event start="T271-731" end="T272-734">čez štiri tedne. [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T274-727" end="T275-472">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T277-208" end="T63">A, mmm veš, </event>
      <event start="T63" end="T62">kaj še morava? </event>
      <event start="T62" end="T280-192">Poden še morava. </event>
      <event start="T280-192" end="T281-143">Tla. </event>
      <event start="T282-094" end="T283-156">Vinil. </event>
      <event start="T283-881" end="T284-884">Sem si ga že ... </event>
      <event start="T286-006" end="T286-533">Ck, ja, </event>
      <event start="T286-533" end="T64">je kar. </event>
      <event start="T64" end="T65">Ni, ni tako poceni. </event>
      <event start="T65" end="T289-497">Veš, kako je. </event>
      <event start="T289-497" end="T291-994">Kvadratni meter tam okrog petindvajset evrov. </event>
      <event start="T296-532" end="T69">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T69" end="T300-685">take velike plošče so, </event>
      <event start="T300-685" end="T301-478">tako v bistvu sem si podobno vzela, tako kot bo pult, kuhinjski, </event>
      <event start="T301-478" end="T301-66">veš? </event>
      <event start="T302-603" end="T303-348">Ja, ja. </event>
      <event start="T304-212" end="T304-937">Ne da? </event>
      <event start="T309-605" end="T310-013">Ej, </event>
      <event start="T310-013" end="T311-927">tako mi je všeč, ko bom imela belo kuhinjo. </event>
      <event start="T312-185" end="T315-387">Pa zdaj sem za rojstni dan dobila bele krožnike. </event>
      <event start="T315-387" end="T316-826">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T316-826" end="T317-611">In bo vse belo. </event>
      <event start="T317-611" end="T75">Kozarce že imam eno leto kupljene doma, </event>
      <event start="T75" end="T322-022">bom imela tudi nove. </event>
      <event start="T322-022" end="T325-115">Za sok pa v() za vodo, kar otroci pijejo. </event>
      <event start="T325-115" end="T325-795">Eee ... </event>
      <event start="T327-079" end="T327-903">Kaj še rabim? </event>
      <event start="T328-478" end="T330-927">Eee premalo prostora bom [smeh] menda imela, </event>
      <event start="T330-927" end="T332-175">glede na to, koliko imam stvari, </event>
      <event start="T332-175" end="T332-948">ne. </event>
      <event start="T333-685" end="T336-797">Včeraj sem eno kuhljo zlomila. </event>
      <event start="T336-797" end="T337-68">Ne včeraj. </event>
      <event start="T339-178" end="T339-765">Ne včeraj, </event>
      <event start="T339-765" end="T341-112">tiste ocvirke pa mast, ko si ti meni dala, </event>
      <event start="T341-112" end="T342-127">veš? </event>
      <event start="T342-682" end="T344-121">Sem ven basala s kuhljo </event>
      <event start="T344-121" end="T346-32">in sem jo zlomila. </event>
      <event start="T346-32" end="T348-987">Pa je bila taka majhna, taka fajna kuhlja. </event>
      <event start="T348-987" end="T350-642">Sem jo kar na pol zlomila. </event>
      <event start="T352-415" end="T353-663">Novo kuhljo. </event>
      <event start="T354-179" end="T356-239">Ampak lesene so mi fajn všeč. </event>
      <event start="T359-612" end="T361-375">Jaz imam tudi plastične </event>
      <event start="T361-375" end="T364-066">pa mislim, da sem lansko leto od tebe za rojstni dan dobila plastično. </event>
      <event start="T364-435" end="T365-061">No. [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T366-412" end="T78">Leseno, </event>
      <event start="T78" end="T368-988">ja, leseno. </event>
      <event start="T368-988" end="T79">Tako da je to, ja, </event>
      <event start="T79" end="T80">tako da bo kar, </event>
      <event start="T80" end="T374-224">zdaj zdaj si že sortiram, kako bom ... </event>
      <event start="T374-224" end="T375-983">V mislih, </event>
      <event start="T375-983" end="T377-243">veš, </event>
      <event start="T377-243" end="T378-393">kam bom kaj dala, ko gledam sliko kuhinje, </event>
      <event start="T378-393" end="T81">kam bom kaj dala, </event>
      <event start="T81" end="T379-931">ne? </event>
      <event start="T380-155" end="T380-893">Kam ... </event>
      <event start="T380-893" end="T82">Ccc, zdaj imam več placa, </event>
      <event start="T82" end="T383-342">ne. </event>
      <event start="T383-342" end="T385-494">Pol bom pa imela manj. </event>
      <event start="T387-963" end="T390-095">Zato ko imam zdaj na tej strani hladilnik, </event>
      <event start="T390-095" end="T391-863">zdaj bo pa vse na eni strani. </event>
      <event start="T392-331" end="T84">In avtomatsko tam ena taka velika omara manjka, </event>
      <event start="T84" end="T395-256">ne? </event>
      <event start="T395-942" end="T396-529">A veš? </event>
      <event start="T396-529" end="T85">Nimam pa tako, ko je bilo včasih, </event>
      <event start="T85" end="T86">še tiste ožje gor, </event>
      <event start="T86" end="T87">veš? </event>
      <event start="T87" end="T400-464">Elemente. </event>
