      <event start="T463" end="T464">skos je, </event>
      <event start="T464" end="T1586-019">no. </event>
      <event start="T1586-019" end="T465">Sicer je res, </event>
      <event start="T465" end="T466">tista prva dva tedna v mescu, </event>
      <event start="T466" end="T1593-159">takr@t delam po deset ur al pa še več. </event>
      <event start="T1594-249" end="T468">Pol pride kakšen teden, k si lahka mal bol razporedim </event>
      <event start="T468" end="T469">pa rečem: </event>
      <event start="T469" end="T470">"Lej, tole bo pa jutr, [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T470" end="T471">pa lahk počaka." [glas] </event>
      <event start="T471" end="T1603-792">Tak da ... </event>
      <event start="T1603-792" end="T1606-966">Odvisno, k@k gre. </event>
      <event start="T1606-966" end="T1608-333">Mhm, mhm. </event>
      <event start="T1609-455" end="T472">Pa mal smo pa šle, </event>
