      <event start="T494" end="T495">na majčka je. </event>
      <event start="T495" end="T1652-032">Ka sem si še pa druga? [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1653-035" end="T496">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T496" end="T1654-711">Ne. </event>
      <event start="T1654-711" end="T497">Ne, ne. </event>
      <event start="T497" end="T498">Točno, </event>
      <event start="T498" end="T1660-054">ene kratke rokave sem si kupla, pa eno tako tri četrt majčko. </event>
      <event start="T1660-054" end="T500">Tko, mal bolj elegantno, </event>
      <event start="T500" end="T501">no, </event>
      <event start="T501" end="T502">tak da, super, fajn, </event>
      <event start="T502" end="T1663-886">ja. </event>
      <event start="T1665-027" end="T504">Drgač pa, </event>
