      <event start="T397" end="T1423-86">karkoli s papirjem ali eee sss sajenje recimo sajenje odzunaj, kakš() karkoli. </event>
      <event start="T1423-86" end="T398">Ni, da ni, </event>
      <event start="T398" end="T1424-625">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1425-093" end="T1426-867">So res take zanimive stvari. </event>
      <event start="T1427-123" end="T400">A ti si veliko na telefonu? </event>
      <event start="T400" end="T1429-933">Kako se tebi zdi? [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1432-588" end="T1433-334">Mhm, mhm. </event>
      <event start="T1434-277" end="T1437-776">Si eee veliko eee na velikih teh omrežjih? </event>
      <event start="T1437-776" end="T1438-846">Recimo Instagram, Facebook pa to. </event>
      <event start="T1438-846" end="T1440-57">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1440-57" end="T1443-099">Kaj je ... TikTok ... </event>
      <event start="T1443-099" end="T1445-6">Saj jih niti ne poznam vseh. </event>
      <event start="T1447-99" end="T1448-894">Ja, ja. </event>
      <event start="T1448-894" end="T1449-203">Ne? </event>
      <event start="T1449-203" end="T1449-423">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1452-249" end="T1452-538">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1453-501" end="T1454-71">Saj jaz tudi ne. </event>
      <event start="T1454-71" end="T1455-67">Jaz sem zelo malo. </event>
      <event start="T1455-67" end="T1461-558">Mogoče včasih se pogovarjaš eee ali od kakšnih sošolk, sošolcev ali kakšnih znancev, </event>
      <event start="T1461-558" end="T1462-759">pol pa lahko pogledaš, </event>
      <event start="T1462-759" end="T411">čakaj, </event>
      <event start="T411" end="T412">kdo pa je to, </event>
      <event start="T412" end="T1463-841">ne? </event>
      <event start="T1464-368" end="T1464-764">Bolj iz tega, </event>
      <event start="T1464-764" end="T1467-847">objavljam nikoli nič ne. </event>
      <event start="T1467-847" end="T1469-365">Ja, ja, ja, ja, ja. </event>
      <event start="T1469-365" end="T416">Tako. </event>
      <event start="T416" end="T417">Ali pa najdeš mogoče kako osebo, ko si jo, </event>
      <event start="T417" end="T418">ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T418" end="T419">v otroštvu poznal, </event>
      <event start="T419" end="T420">pa nimaš stikov </event>
      <event start="T420" end="T421">pa bi napletel stike, </event>
      <event start="T421" end="T422">pa najdeš, </event>
      <event start="T422" end="T1478-967">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1478-967" end="T1479-882">Tudi lahko. </event>
      <event start="T1481-757" end="T1482-74">Ja, ja, ja. </event>
      <event start="T1482-74" end="T1484-06">Veš da, veš da, </event>
      <event start="T1484-06" end="T1484-504">veš da. </event>
      <event start="T1487-746" end="T1489-244">Je ogromno, ne? </event>
      <event start="T1490-096" end="T1491-582">Veš da, veš da. </event>
      <event start="T1491-582" end="T1494-445">A veš, kaj pa delava midva tamle na travniku? </event>
      <event start="T1494-445" end="T1496-528">Za kresovanje. </event>
      <event start="T1497-02" end="T1497-543">Sta bl() </event>
      <event start="T1497-543" end="T1498-704">ste bili lani tudi? </event>
      <event start="T1498-704" end="T429">Pri nas, ne? </event>
      <event start="T429" end="T1501-122">Boste letos spet prišli? </event>
      <event start="T1501-966" end="T430">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T430" end="T431">zdaj obrezujeva drevje </event>
      <event start="T431" end="T1505-029">pa ne vem, kaj še vse, </event>
      <event start="T1505-029" end="T1506-595">pa na koliko ... </event>
      <event start="T1506-595" end="T433">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T433" end="T1508-715">tridesetega aprila. </event>
      <event start="T1509-686" end="T1512-67">Pol bomo pa spet kakšen piknik naredili prej. </event>
      <event start="T1514-077" end="T1515-02">Ja, ja. </event>
      <event start="T1517-818" end="T1520-24">[smeh] Neke narezke, </event>
      <event start="T1520-24" end="T439">pa to s trak() eee z enim tako muto ali kaj, </event>
      <event start="T439" end="T1523-284">ne? </event>
      <event start="T1523-811" end="T440">Ja, ja. [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T440" end="T1527-489">Saj je bilo luštno, </event>
      <event start="T1527-489" end="T1528-789">ja. </event>
      <event start="T1529-95" end="T1531-072">Aha, aha, </event>
      <event start="T1531-072" end="T1531-896">pa Elica. [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1531-896" end="T1533-64">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1534-314" end="T1536-133">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1536-889" end="T1537-198">Fajn. </event>
      <event start="T1543-915" end="T446">Ja, ja, ja, </event>
      <event start="T446" end="T1545-501">veš da, veš da. </event>
      <event start="T1545-969" end="T447">Ta vaša, </event>
      <event start="T447" end="T1547-011">ne? </event>
      <event start="T1547-649" end="T448">Ja, ja, </event>
      <event start="T448" end="T1549-809">k sta fajna. </event>
      <event start="T1549-809" end="T1550-693">Bi bilo super, </event>
      <event start="T1550-693" end="T1551-121">ne? </event>
      <event start="T1554-212" end="T450">Ahh, </event>
      <event start="T450" end="T1555-599">glej. </event>
      <event start="T1555-599" end="T1558-682">Zarečenega kruha se največ poje. </event>
      <event start="T1558-682" end="T1561-813">[smeh] Aja. </event>
      <event start="T1563-034" end="T1563-553">Aja, </event>
      <event start="T1563-553" end="T452">glej, </event>
      <event start="T452" end="T453">pride, pride tak dan, </event>
      <event start="T453" end="T454">a veš? </event>
      <event start="T454" end="T1566-577">Tako da ... </event>
      <event start="T1566-577" end="T455">Vse fajn, </event>
      <event start="T455" end="T456">super, fajn, </event>
      <event start="T456" end="T1568-392">ja. </event>
      <event start="T1568-991" end="T1572-384">Ja. [glas] </event>
      <event start="T1573-585" end="T1575-4">[smeh] Mora biti. </event>
      <event start="T1578-471" end="T1580-592">Ahh. [glas] </event>
      <event start="T1582-249" end="T461">Eem, </event>
      <event start="T461" end="T462">ja, </event>
      <event start="T462" end="T460">je kar, </event>
      <event start="T460" end="T463">skozi je, </event>
      <event start="T463" end="T464">skozi je, </event>
      <event start="T464" end="T1586-019">no. </event>
      <event start="T1586-019" end="T465">Sicer je res, </event>
      <event start="T465" end="T466">tista prva dva tedna v mesecu, </event>
      <event start="T466" end="T1593-159">takrat delam po deset ur ali pa še več. </event>
      <event start="T1594-249" end="T468">Pol pride kakšen teden, k si lahko malo bolj razporedim </event>
      <event start="T468" end="T469">pa rečem: </event>
      <event start="T469" end="T470">"Glej, tole bo pa jutri, [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T470" end="T471">pa lahko počaka." [glas] </event>
      <event start="T471" end="T1603-792">Tako da ... </event>
      <event start="T1603-792" end="T1606-966">Odvisno, kako gre. </event>
      <event start="T1606-966" end="T1608-333">Mhm, mhm. </event>
      <event start="T1609-455" end="T472">Pa malo smo pa šle, </event>
      <event start="T472" end="T473">v Europark smo šle, </event>
      <event start="T473" end="T1614-306">neki() dve stvari sem si pa kupila. </event>
      <event start="T1615-844" end="T477">Ja, no, </event>
      <event start="T477" end="T476">glej, </event>
      <event start="T476" end="T478">če že greš, </event>
      <event start="T478" end="T1617-124">ne? </event>
      <event start="T1618-028" end="T479">Pa če najdeš kaj. </event>
      <event start="T479" end="T480">Čeprav pa vseeno, </event>
      <event start="T480" end="T481">no. </event>
      <event start="T481" end="T1624-242">Peek() eee tale PeekAndCloppenburg smo šle. </event>
      <event start="T1626-117" end="T1626-624">Pa ja, </event>
      <event start="T1626-624" end="T1627-575">se mi zdi, da ... </event>
      <event start="T1628-487" end="T482">Pa ja, </event>
      <event start="T482" end="T483">včeraj se mi je zdelo izredno, </event>
      <event start="T483" end="T484">neka sprememba, </event>
      <event start="T484" end="T1633-255">no. </event>
      <event start="T1633-255" end="T1634-408">Že dolgo nisem šla. </event>
      <event start="T1634-408" end="T485">Ja, ja. </event>
      <event start="T485" end="T486">Tako da, </event>
      <event start="T486" end="T487">res, </event>
      <event start="T487" end="T1637-353">cene grejo gor. </event>
      <event start="T1638-177" end="T488">Tako redko grem, </event>
      <event start="T488" end="T489">če mi le ni treba, </event>
      <event start="T489" end="T1640-963">glej. </event>
      <event start="T1640-963" end="T1642-073">[nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T1642-073" end="T490">In kaj sem si kupila? </event>
      <event start="T490" end="T1643-737">Kaj sem si kupila, </event>
      <event start="T1643-737" end="T1647-038">[glas] saj ni nič kaj posebnega. </event>
      <event start="T1647-038" end="T492">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T492" end="T493">no, </event>
      <event start="T493" end="T494">majčka je, </event>
      <event start="T494" end="T495">ena majčka je. </event>
      <event start="T495" end="T1652-032">Kaj sem si še pa drugega? [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1653-035" end="T496">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T496" end="T1654-711">Ne. </event>
      <event start="T1654-711" end="T497">Ne, ne. </event>
      <event start="T497" end="T498">Točno, </event>
      <event start="T498" end="T1660-054">ene kratke rokave sem si kupila, pa eno tako tri četrt majčko. </event>
      <event start="T1660-054" end="T500">Tako, malo bolj elegantno, </event>
      <event start="T500" end="T501">no, </event>
      <event start="T501" end="T502">tako da, super, fajn, </event>
      <event start="T502" end="T1663-886">ja. </event>
      <event start="T1665-027" end="T504">Drugače pa, </event>
      <event start="T504" end="T505">glej, </event>
      <event start="T505" end="T506">mogoče pa naslednjič. </event>
      <event start="T506" end="T507">Včasih greš v trgovino </event>
      <event start="T507" end="T1670-239">pa najdeš ... </event>
      <event start="T1671-65" end="T508">Takoj najdeš, </event>
      <event start="T508" end="T509">glej, </event>
      <event start="T509" end="T510">pa ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T510" end="T511">pa si kupiš takoj pet stvari, </event>
      <event start="T511" end="T512">drugič pa boš hodil, </event>
      <event start="T512" end="T513">pa ne boš nič našel za sebe, </event>
      <event start="T513" end="T1678-102">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1678-689" end="T1680-161">Kako naletiš. </event>
      <event start="T1682-016" end="T1682-957">A res da? </event>
      <event start="T1683-306" end="T514">O, </event>
      <event start="T514" end="T1688-422">a nisi si že ne() pred kratkim? [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1688-989" end="T1689-837">Čisto bele? </event>
      <event start="T1690-888" end="T1693-38">Z onim debelejšim podplatom? </event>
      <event start="T1693-669" end="T1694-521">Ja, ja, </event>
